Package: argufy
Title: Declerative Arguments Checks
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Gabor Csardi, Jim Hester
Maintainer: Gabor Csardi <csardi.gabor@gmail.com>
Description: Declare your functions with argument checks, and 'argufy' will
    generate and add the checking code for you.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/gaborcsardi/argufy
BugReports: https://github.com/gaborcsardi/argufy/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports:
    methods
Suggests:
    testthat,
    disposables
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
